Subject Barley ** August 2010 - January 2011 INITIAL PAYMENTS **
PrecisOrder a) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2010-947 of July 19, 2010; and b) approving the increase by the Canadian Wheat Board of the initial payments for grades other than the base grade of BARLEY for the pool period beginning on August 1, 2010 and ending on January 31, 2011.
